CREATE TABLE Partnerships (
    partnership_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    organization_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    partnership_start_date DATE NOT NULL,
    partnership_end_date DATE,
    partnership_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	organization_name VARCHAR(255),
	partner_name VARCHAR(255),
	partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
	partnership_start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	organization_name VARCHAR(255),
	collaborator_name VARCHAR(255),
	collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
	collaboration_start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
  collab_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  collab_name VARCHAR(50),
  collab_type VARCHAR(50),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE stakeholders (
  stakeholder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  stakeholder_name VARCHAR(50),
  stakeholder_type VARCHAR(50),
  contact_person VARCHAR(50),
  contact_email VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    organization_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partnership_type VARCHAR(100),
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    organization_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaborator_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(100),
    collaboration_start_date DATE,
    collaboration_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE stakeholders (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stakeholder_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_person VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE activities (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_name VARCHAR(255),
    activity_description TEXT,
    activity_date DATE,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (stakeholder_id) REFERENCES stakeholders(id)
);

CREATE TABLE partners (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner_type VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_description TEXT,
    collaboration_start_date DATE,
    collaboration_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE community_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    project_description TEXT,
    project_start_date DATE,
    project_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE project_partners (
    project_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (project_id, partner_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES community_projects(project_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES partners(partner_id)
)

CREATE TABLE project_collaborations (
    project_id INT,
    collaboration_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (project_id, collaboration_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES community_projects(project_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (collaboration_id) REFERENCES collaborations(collaboration_id)
)
